cn.domob.android.ads
类 DomobInterstitialAd

java.lang.Object
  cn.domob.android.ads.DomobInterstitialAd

public class DomobInterstitialAd
extends java.lang.Object

A class for invoking Domob interstitial ads.

Calls and displays interstitial ads through invoking this class.。

DomobInterstitialAd

public DomobInterstitialAd(android.content.Context context,
                           java.lang.String publisherID,
                           java.lang.String placementID,
                           java.lang.String size)
Constructor for interstitial ad

参数：
context -
publisherID - publisher ID from official site of Domob
placementID - placement ID from official site of Domob
size - size for requesting corresponding ad, generally set with a constant in DomobAdview, adjusting according the density of screen. Please refer to the user guide for details.

DomobInterstitialAd

public DomobInterstitialAd(android.content.Context context,
                           java.lang.String publisherID,
                           java.lang.String placementID,
                           java.lang.String size,
                           DomobInterstitialAd.BorderType borderType)
Constructor for interstitial ad using built-in border

参数：
context -
publisherID - publisher ID from official site of Domob
placementID - placement ID from official site of Domob
size - for requesting corresponding ad, generally set with a constant in DomobAdview, adjusting according the density of screen. Please refer to the user guide for details.
borderType - BorderType.Black, BorderType.White, BorderType.None. Please refer to the user guide for details.

DomobInterstitialAd

public DomobInterstitialAd(android.content.Context context,
                           java.lang.String publisherID,
                           java.lang.String placementID,
                           java.lang.String size,
                           int resId,
                           int width,
                           int height)
Constructor for interstitial ad using customized border

参数：
context -
publisherID - publisher ID from official site of Domob
placementID - placement ID from official site of Domob
size - size for requesting corresponding ad, generally set with a constant in DomobAdview, adjusting according the density of screen. Please refer to the user guide for details.
resId - resource id for customized border
width - logical width for customized border. Please refer to the user guide for details.
height - logical height for customized border. Please refer to the user guide for details.
